      "title": "<span id=\"#84\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">absorb</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(v.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>\"吸收，吮吸，通过吸收吸入\"，15世纪初，来自古法语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">absorbir</span>， <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">assorbir</span>（13世纪，现代法语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">absorber</span>），源自拉丁语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">absorbere</span> “吞噬，吞下”，由 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">ab</span> “离开，远离”（见 <a href=\"/cn/word/ab-\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of ab- \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\">ab-</a>)和 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">sorbere</span> “吸入”组成，源自 PIE 词根 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">*srebh-</span> “吸，吸收”（源头还包括亚美尼亚语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">arbi</span> “我喝了”，希腊语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">rhopheo</span> “贪婪地喝，狼吞虎咽”，立陶宛语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">srebiu, srėbti</span> “贪婪地喝”）。比喻意义上的“完全吸引（某人的）注意力”始于1763年。</p><ins class=\"adsbygoogle relative inline-block transition-all inline-block h-[250px] w-[300px]\" data-ad-slot=\"4000736339\" data-adtest=\"off\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"></ins>"
    }
